snippet: An aspiring professional surfer and model in Hawaii has been charged with attempted murder over accusations she rammed her car into an elderly woman at the parking garage of a Waikiki apartment complex, prosecutors said on Monday....

headline.print_headline: Aspiring Pro Surfer Charged With Attempted Murder in Hawaii
headline.main: Aspiring Pro Surfer Charged With Attempted Murder in Hawaii

lead_paragraph: An aspiring professional surfer and model in Hawaii has been charged with attempted murder over accusations she rammed her car into an elderly woman at the parking garage of a Waikiki apartment complex, prosecutors said on Monday.
